filtersql: SELECT COUNT(*) from info_type AS it1 WHERE it1.id in ('1')
SELECT COUNT(*) from company_type AS ct WHERE ct.kind in ('distributors')

SELECT COUNT(*) from title AS t WHERE t.production_year <= 1975 AND t.production_year >= 1925
